  "asset_name": "echo_hungry",
  "category": "character",
  "subcategory": "echo_state",
  "description": "Create Echo hungry state loop animation as a horizontal sprite strip. Echo sprite frame size is 40x40px. Primary body color #FFA300, cheek patch #FF004D, crest #FFEC27, beak+feet #AB5236, eyes #1D2B53. Eyes are 2x2px blocks. No additional colors beyond the pico8_16 palette. No anti-aliasing; 1px steps only. Animation: 4 frames, 2 FPS, loop infinite. Spritesheet 160x40px. Gaze direction: beak points down-left toward the food bowl position; shift beak tip left by -2px from idle in all frames. Frames 2 and 4: add a 1px vertical bounce (body y+1px) to suggest impatience. Do not include any speech bubble in this spritesheet; bubble is a UI asset.",
